Name: Cripsy Juicy Fried Pork Chops Lunchbox
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 30%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A generously packed lunchbox loaded with flavor. Take a firm bite of the golden, crispy pork chops and savor every last piece. The satisfaction and energy it gives you will fuel your next victory!
